Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.40,0:09:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是中枢部的警备系统 特别的严密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.60,0:09:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.50,0:09:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为稍微抢先了一步呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.40,0:09:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们挺能干的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.40,0:09:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你先替我们帮引擎热身啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.50,0:09:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Alv
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.70,0:09:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对贵族来说 这个对策算是又快又适当的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.90,0:09:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是贵族 是我自己的判断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.50,0:09:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是背叛吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.00,0:09:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为你们的能力只有Absorb(吸收并复制) 看来我好像是错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.50,0:09:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Alv 已经到了这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.00,0:09:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要再无谓地杀人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.10,0:09:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳想命令我吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.20,0:09:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Alv
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.40,0:09:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.10,0:10:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Alv
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.10,0:10:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经到了这里 不需要只会说废话的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.80,0:10:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对自己的母亲也下得了手吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.20,0:10:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长...官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.60,0:10:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳早就知道了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.60,0:10:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就知道?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.30,0:10:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知是自己的母亲还开枪吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.70,0:10:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.40,0:10:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屏壁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.20,0:10:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个能源当开胃菜正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.80,0:10:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都能吸收的能力?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.20,0:10:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼 结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.30,0:11:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什...什么? 重力之井?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.70,0:11:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这...这里...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事? 什么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.10,0:11:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.90,0:11:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reception system chamber(吸收系统)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.20,0:11:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用机器重现你们能力的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.40,0:11:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A...Alv
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.80,0:11:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分解，吸收任何东西，转换为能源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.80,0:11:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这艘船的能源炉之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.10,0:11:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.40,0:11:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.10,0:12:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Alv
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.50,0:12:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,La Muse试作0号舰卡利俄铂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.80,0:12:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾状纳米机械组成的大气 可能是某种屏壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.30,0:12:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请注意干涉波的冲击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.60,0:12:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.30,0:12:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.30,0:12:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要到机器堆里去对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.80,0:12:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使能力不能用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.90,0:12:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的工具还是可以派上用场的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.10,0:12:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.00,0:12:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那个时候开始已经等了半个世纪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.10,0:12:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇巴耶特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.20,0:12:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀啊呀 用不着从那种地方进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.20,0:13:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于你们 我会敞开大门恭候光临的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.60,0:13:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多托利修克长官 凭借GOTT ES成员的权力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.30,0:13:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们以星际犯罪者的罪名告发你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.10,0:13:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所做的行为 违反宇宙行星联盟宪章，以及银河星际航行规约等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.60,0:13:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总共317条罪行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.40,0:13:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是317件 应该是做了超过80000件的罪行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.90,0:13:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到目前为止的这段时间里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.80,0:13:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.30,0:13:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一件一件说出来太麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.10,0:13:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详细内容和证据刚才传送到整个银河系中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.00,0:13:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,违反联盟宪章等等 可说是罄竹难书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.20,0:13:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些资料显示的很明显是违法行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.60,0:13:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在让人震惊 将自己置身于企业、司法、政治之上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.40,0:13:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很明显是背叛社会正义的行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.70,0:14:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些数据有极高证据力 现在通过银河网络以量子情报方式共享
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.90,0:14:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做什么? 目的是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.50,0:14:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair 因为我想要救妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.60,0:14:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得我吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.80,0:14:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.50,0:14:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不可能忘掉 这50年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.40,0:14:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀啊呀 肚子饿了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.20,0:14:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算摸这里 我也没有奶可以喂你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.60,0:14:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么GOTT 什么宇宙行星联合 我..我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.10,0:14:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 不要紧吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.90,0:15:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是妈妈哦 不是一直告诉你吗 叫我Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.90,0:15:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不是Eclair真正的孩子吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.80,0:15:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.40,0:15:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.80,0:15:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使没有血缘，你也是我可爱的儿子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.50,0:15:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你大概不知道有你在身边，对我而言是多大的救赎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.80,0:15:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.10,0:15:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.80,0:15:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总有一天会忘了我，离我而去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.50,0:15:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.90,0:15:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请过上幸福的生活 你有这个权力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.50,0:15:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是地球人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.60,0:15:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我早就知道你是贵族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.00,0:16:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair 我不会忘 绝对不会忘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.70,0:16:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天我会长成能够保护妳的大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.10,0:16:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天 一定...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.50,0:16:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天开始成为多托利修克家的一员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.40,0:16:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇巴耶特．多托利修克 请做符合你这个身份的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.70,0:16:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.70,0:16:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的贵族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.00,0:16:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair ES成员 银河通商关税机构
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.70,0:16:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 调查东西吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.20,0:16:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.40,0:16:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是老样子 是个爱学习的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.90,0:16:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 理想决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.40,0:16:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要成为政治家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.00,0:16:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于欧莫乌诺星系 行星阿兹蓝迪雅第二次的灾害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.10,0:17:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相关各国共同对外发表了再开发计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.20,0:17:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个银河面临着一场真正的能源经济革命浪潮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.70,0:17:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由此 宇宙行星联盟经济署也做了世代交替
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.20,0:17:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新任领导是奇巴耶特．多托利修克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.00,0:17:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另兼任GOTT长官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.80,0:17:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇巴耶特 你大概知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.10,0:17:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近庶民们开始多了不必要的智慧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.70,0:17:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都拜托你了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.50,0:17:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.20,0:17:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢卡利翁 这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.10,0:17:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair 听说是丧失了记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.00,0:17:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.30,0:17:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 为什么这么做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.20,0:18:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.00,0:18:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船是贵族们背叛全银河的人民所制造的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.80,0:18:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅不满10万人的旧家族 纯粹的地球人种-贵族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.70,0:18:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用合法或非法手段聚集的资产所建造受诅咒的宇宙船-丢卡利翁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.40,0:18:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的贵族准备乘这艘船 带着整个地球逃到别的银河去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.30,0:18:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个地球? 这种事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.60,0:18:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船的话就有可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.40,0:18:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.60,0:18:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河系所有经济崩遗 混乱的话会怎么样呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.70,0:18:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由行星环境改造系统人工制造、维持着的各个脆弱的行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.60,0:18:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻就会无法住人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.10,0:18:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.80,0:18:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船甚至还周详到写入了破坏所有空间跳跃口的程序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.70,0:18:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着启动仪式接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.30,0:19:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐渐解除伪装的这艘船本身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.40,0:19:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是无法动摇的铁证
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.80,0:19:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能防范于未然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.90,0:19:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起诉时已经晚了的犯罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.50,0:19:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我要做的事就全部完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.70,0:19:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在立刻停止播放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.00,0:19:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在全银河网络做了量子播放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.30,0:19:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.20,0:19:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话将会发生全银河规模的暴动...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.10,0:19:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟罗森费尔特一派联络的频道还保留着吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.20,0:19:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.60,0:19:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要采取与庶民融合的方案吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.60,0:19:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有都结束了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.40,0:19:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来贵族事实上算是消失了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.30,0:19:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他们不会放过做了这种事的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.80,0:19:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair 可以的话 由妳的手来...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.30,0:19:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇巴耶特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.00,0:19:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望不是其它人 而是由妳来终结我的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.30,0:20:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 在这之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.90,0:20:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期望叫妳一声"妈妈" 一直...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.70,0:20:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信长大后如果能把妳从贵族的控制下救出的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.80,0:20:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以实现这个愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.00,0:20:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇巴耶特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.10,0:20:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经满足了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.90,0:20:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.00,0:20:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈?
